parameters.text:
=Generate platform-specific social media content for Instagram, Facebook, and Pinterest in a single JSON object.

Post Inputs:
- Topic: {{ $('Get Next Scheduled Post').item.json.Topic }}
- Angle / Question: {{ $('Get Next Scheduled Post').item.json['Question / Angle'] }}

Brand & Product Context:
{
  "client_name": "<COMPANY-NAME>",
  "industry": "<COMPANY-INDUSTRY>",
  "product_source_url": "<COMPANY-INDUSTRY>",
  "product_type": "<PRODUCT-TYPE>",
  "brand_tone": "<BRAND-TONE>"
}

OUTPUT FORMAT (JSON ONLY):

{
  "instagram": {
    "post_content": "<string>",
    "hashtags": ["#...", "#..."]
  }
}

Rules:
- Captions MUST be unique per platform.
- Captions MUST NOT include hashtags.
- Reference the brand/product subtly to maintain natural engagement.
- Pinterest captions should be SEO-rich and benefit-driven.
- Use trending keywords only if they fit naturally.
- Return ONLY the JSON structure ‚Äî no commentary.

